title: GI.Joe.The.Rise.Of.Cobra[2009] and GI Joe Retaliation [2013]
description:
G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra (2009) DVD Rip Eng. Subs.


An elite military unit comprised of special operatives known as the G.I. Joes, operating out of The Pit, takes on an evil organization led by a notorious arms dealer.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

G.I. Joe: Retaliation (2013) Cam version (not the greatest quality but it's decent enough to watch and understand and the audio is in sync)

The G.I. Joes are not only fighting their mortal enemy Cobra; they are forced to contend with threats from within the government that jeopardize their very existence.
